arrangement: This stunning arrangement has it all. Beautiful yellow cymbidium orchids, brilliant bi-color roses and tropical leaves all hand-delivered in a striking Couture Vase. It's definitely a departure from the everyday!

name: Teleflora's Uptown Bouquet
description: An arrangement worthy of your uptown girl, this one rocks! Modern without being trendy. Gorgeous without being girly. If your woman knows style, this is the gift for her.
arrangement: Outrageously beautiful dark orange and peach roses are nestled in a garden of greens and delivered in a unique bamboo rectangle. Go ahead: show her that you get it.

name: Goodness And Light Bouquet
description: Add a healthy dose of goodness and light to someone's day with this colorful bouquet! Its bountiful blend of alstroemeria, stock and asters in cheerful shades of pink, yellow and lavender is sure to make them smile.
arrangement: This beautiful bouquet includes red alstroemeria, light yellow carnations, pink stock, hot pink matsumoto asters, large lavender monte cassino asters, yellow button spray chrysanthemums, bupleurum, huckleberry, and parvifolia eucalyptus. Delivered in a clear cylinder vase.

name: Teleflora's Pop Of Fun Bouquet
description: Turn up the fun! Make any day extra special with a surprise delivery of joyful blooms in a stylish cube vase. This bouquet of pink roses and luxurious peach lilies will make their mood soar!
arrangement: This fresh, fun mix of pink roses, peach asiatic lilies, peach alstroemeria, pink carnations and pink miniature carnations is accented with raspberry sinuata statice and leatherleaf fern. Delivered in a glass cube.

name: Hello Beautiful Bouquet
description: Take their breath away with the beautiful hello that this bouquet brings! A wildly sophisticated array of pale pink roses and lilies with modern greens, it's perfectly presented in a simple white square vase.
arrangement: This feminine bouquet includes light pink spray roses, light pink asiatic lilies, pink alstroemeria, pink carnations, pink larkspur, white sinuata statice, dusty miller, israeli ruscus, huckleberry, seeded eucalyptus, lemon leaf, and a large green potted echeveria succulent. Delivered in a white square vase.

name: Teleflora's Exotic Grace
description: Looking for something with a bit of Zen? With tall bamboo and birds of paradise complemented by a stunning mix of tropical orange flowers and greenery in a graceful bamboo container, this bouquet is it.
arrangement: Birds of paradise, asiatic lilies, alstroemeria, red hypercium, accented with ti and galax leaves arrive in a beautifully exotic keepsake bamboo container.

name: Teleflora's Tropical Bliss
description: Now this is bliss! This tropical and tasteful creation is a beautiful and dramatic way to say something wonderful without using any words.
arrangement: Dark red roses, orange asiatic lilies, green leucadendron, yellow button spray chrysanthemums, and tropical greens are delivered in a red bamboo dish. Don't miss this chance to send bliss!

name: Make Me Blush - Dozen Long Stemmed Pink Roses
description: It's fun to be flirty! Send a dozen roses to the one you love and she just might make you blush. Especially if the dozen roses in question are this gorgeous! This arrangement is sweet and innocent as can be. Of course, it's a bit sassy and a whole lot sexy, as well.
arrangement: Sending a dozen perfectly pink roses and white limonium arranged in a glass vase to the woman you love shows that you know how much fun love is! And every woman appreciates that!

name: Teleflora's Delicate Dozen
description: As soft and delicate as the first blush of love, this rose bouquet carries a lot of romance.
arrangement: Gorgeous sweet pink roses arranged in a clear glass vase sends such a beautiful message of love, it just might leave you and your love blushing.

name: Dreaming in Pink - Long Stemmed Pink Roses
description: Women really appreciate it when their guys think outside of the box. There's nothing like hot pink roses to prove that you're using your imagination and aren't afraid to let her know.

name: Rosy Glow Bouquet

name: Teleflora's Birthday Sparkle Bouquet
description: Add some extra special sparkle to their birthday with this grand gift! Hand-delivered in a shimmering golden cube with intricate cutouts, this colorful bouquet will make their birthday week wonderful. Later, they can remove the pretty magenta liner and golden "happy birthday" pick and enjoy the cube as a pretty candleholder!
arrangement: This colorful mix features orange roses, orange spray roses, fuchsia stock, pink carnations, spiral eucalyptus and lemon leaf. Delivered in a Celebrate in Style cube.

name: Basket Full of Wishes
description: Wishes do come true, by the basketful, actually. This delightful arrangement is so full of sunny blossoms, it even includes a pretty yellow butterfly who obviously feels right at home, basking in the warmth.
arrangement: Brilliant yellow spray roses, asiatic lilies, miniature gerberas, carnations, alstroemeria, button spray chrysanthemums and delightful greenery are joined by a delicate butterfly in an oval basket. It's a basket of wonder and wishes!
